{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "第十四回\"南宫丑的秘密\"：梅汝男向郭大路等人坦白身世，揭露黑衣人并非南宫丑而是其兄梅汝甲。梅家虽为武林世家，实则外强中干，梅汝甲为报家族仇怨并解决经济困境，冒充南宫丑混入棍子和金狮子的队伍。梅汝男暗中帮助郭大路等人，送棺材告知林太平所杀之人未死。最终梅汝男巧妙地让四人承诺帮助她解决困难，暗示选择其中一人作为\"妹夫\"带回家应对哥哥，以聪明狡黠的方式将众人套住。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想，梅汝男会不会是梅汝甲的妹妹呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是不是都和我没关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "梅家是不是和风栖梧有仇？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不问她自己去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她自己既然没有说，我问也问不出的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你是不敢问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怕得罪她，怕她生气，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来得倒真巧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许因为他喜欢你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许就因为他已看出你喜欢的人不是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想问的你的那些事，你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在为什么不告诉我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怕你听了吃不下饭去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以后呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "以后的事，你们就全都猜错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们猜错了哪些事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第一，那黑衣人并不是南宫丑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是南宫丑是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是我哥哥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你们不但想要风栖梧的命，还想要他的钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他是我哥哥的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不坐在这里在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "躺着，就算没有躺在棺材里，至少也躺在床上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "直到我无意中看到了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上也许只有一种人比他更痛苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪种人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的妹妹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那口棺材是你送来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为的是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论如何，我总不能出卖我哥哥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你一直不敢露面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的人呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回家了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你把他救走的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是我，他是我嫡亲的哥哥，我总不能看着他受苦……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说她错了，谁就是混蛋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只能说她简直不是个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也比不上？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若换了我，我倒真未必敢将这种事当面说出来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非但不差劲，简直伟大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怪你？谁敢怪你？我们简直应该跪下来给你磕头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不是你，我们就算没有被毒死，也饿死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我哥哥也并不是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也用不着为他解释，我们也不怪他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我若是他说不定也会这么样做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我做得也许比他更凶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他现在就已知道。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他知道后怎么样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "气得要命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么办？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就溜了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你迟早总要回去的，那是你的家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个女孩子嫁了人之后，就可以不必回娘家。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以她就不能不赶快出嫁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嫁给谁呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_tai_ping",
      "speaker_name": "林太平",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要王老大一句话，我还有什么问题？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你若有什么困难，为什么还不说出来呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你只管说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只好说是他的妹夫，因为我已和这人订亲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "带什么回去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_ru_nan",
      "speaker_name": "梅汝男",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "带人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_dong",
      "speaker_name": "王动",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "带什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
